https://www.baeldung.com/spring-boot-keycloak

GIT: https://github.com/eugenp/tutorials/tree/master/spring-boot-modules/spring-boot-keycloak

keycloak userguide: https://www.keycloak.org/docs/13.0/getting_started/

hanle SSL certificate:

sudo keytool -importcert -alias local-CA -keystore /usr/lib/jvm/jre-11-openjdk-11.0.14.1.1-2.el8_5.x86_64/lib/security/cacerts -file keycloak_server.pem

pass: changeit

